The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) has appointed a team of Technical Advisers to the PDP Presidential candidate in the 2019 general elections, Atiku Abubakar.
Director of Media and Publicity, PDP Presidential Campaign Organization, Kola Ologbondiyan, in a statement in Abuja indicated that the Technical Advisers include:
His Excellency, Mallam Sule Lamido
His Excellency, Senator Ahmed Makarfi
His Excellency, Hon. Yakubu Dogara
His Excellency, Senator Ike Ekweremmadu
Sule Lamido was also named Chairman of Elder’s Council for the PDP campaign.
Also, Alhaji Kawu Baraje has been appointed Technical Adviser to the Director General of the PDP Presidential Campaign Council, President of the Senate, Abubakar Bukola Saraki, while Dr. Doyin Okupe was appointed Media Adviser to the Director General, Saraki.


